schools.name: West Prepatory Academy At Charlles I West Hall Sec

data.description: Beautiful 1 story, 2 Bedrooms plus den/office (possible 3rd bedroom) & 2 baths home with NO HOA. No Neighbors behind. Tile wood flooring throughout. White shaker cabinets, farmhouse sink and quartz counters in kitchen with beautiful backsplash. Kitchen also features a pantry! and baths. Ceiling fans in bedrooms. Updated baths as well ! Stainless steel appliances. Covered patio. Large primary bedroom with walk in closet. Solar heating!
